    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: 'This is an example scene of Fax Analytics.

    Every X seconds, it checks if the player is in the left

    area, right area, or in-between.

    It tracks if the players falls off the map (once),

    and how many times the blue button has been pressed.


    There''s also a survey to ask players what they think of

    the world. It contains some basic error handling, too.


    This example scene uses Google Forms for analytics.

    From there the data can be exported to a spreadsheet.'
